@startuml

title Agent Publishing - Sequence Diagram

autonumber

actor "Developer" as Developer
actor "AI Architect" as Architect
participant "AI Portal" as Portal
participant "Agent Registry" as Registry
participant "Governance Service" as Governance
participant "Evaluation Service" as Evaluation
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Audit Service" as Audit

Developer -> Portal: Create or update agent
Portal -> Registry: Save draft version
Registry -> Kafka: Publish agent.updated
Developer -> Portal: Submit for review
Portal -> Governance: Submit agent version
Governance -> Evaluation: Run required evaluations
Evaluation --> Governance: Evaluation results
Architect -> Portal: Review risk, quality and compliance
Portal -> Governance: Approve version
Governance -> Registry: Mark version as published
Governance -> Kafka: Publish governance.approved
Governance -> Kafka: Publish agent.published
Kafka -> Audit: Consume governance and agent events
Portal --> Developer: Version published

@enduml
